message.content: ∀ (E : ℕ → ℕ), (∀ n, E n = ∑ i in Finset.range n, i * (n.factorization 5)) → Filter.Tendsto (fun n => E n / n^2) Filter.atTop (nhds (1 / 8))

∀ (E : ℕ → ℕ),
  (∀ n, E n = ∑ i in Finset.range (n + 1), i * (n.choose i).factorization 5) →
  Filter.Tendsto (fun n => (E n : ℝ) / n^2) Filter.atTop (nhds (1 / 8))
∀ (n : ℕ), Filter.Tendsto (fun n => (∑ i in Finset.range (n + 1), i * Nat.log 5 (i))) / n^2 Filter.atTop (nhds (1 / 8))
∀ (E : ℕ → ℕ), (∀ n, E n = (Finset.range n).sum (fun k => k * Nat.factorization (n.choose k) 5)) → Filter.Tendsto (fun n => ↑(E n) / n ^ 2) Filter.atTop (nhds (1 / 8))

∀ (E : ℕ → ℕ), (∀ n, E n = ∑ k in Finset.range (n + 1), (n / 5 ^ k) - (k / 5 ^ k)) → 
Filter.Tendsto (fun n => E n / n ^ 2) Filter.atTop (nhds (1 / 8))
∀ (E : ℕ → ℕ), Filter.Tendsto (fun n => E n / n ^ 2) Filter.atTop (nhds (1 / 8))

∀ (E : ℕ → ℕ), (∀ n, E n = ∑ k in Finset.range n, n.factorization 5) →
  Filter.Tendsto (fun n => E n / n ^ 2) Filter.atTop (nhds (1 / 8))
∀ (E : ℕ → ℕ), (∀ n, E n = ∑ i in Finset.range n, i * (n / 5 ^ i)) → Filter.Tendsto (fun n => E n / n ^ 2) Filter.atTop (nhds (1 / 8))

∀ (E : ℕ → ℕ), (∀ n, E n = ∑ k in Finset.range (n + 1), (k * (n.factorization 5).choose k)) →
  Filter.Tendsto (fun n => E n / n^2) Filter.atTop (nhds (1 / 8))

∀ (E : ℕ → ℕ), (∀ n, E n = ∑ i in Finset.range (n + 1), i * (n.factorization 5)) →
  Tendsto (fun n => E n / n^2) Filter.atTop (nhds (1 / 8))
